01:09:10.733 --> 01:09:13.100
Look, I saw Mom and Dad
the night they died.

01:09:14.233 --> 01:09:16.367
Oh it had been
years, and I figured

01:09:16.367 --> 01:09:17.933
I tried to patch
things up with them,

01:09:17.933 --> 01:09:19.966
See if I could salvage anything,

01:09:19.966 --> 01:09:22.700
But, when I saw them,

01:09:23.733 --> 01:09:25.367
Dad started drinking

01:09:25.367 --> 01:09:28.067
