01:09:30.733 --> 01:09:32.466
So I tried to make him stop,

01:09:32.466 --> 01:09:34.733
But, of course he wouldn't.

01:09:35.567 --> 01:09:37.067
Then I tried to take Mom away,

01:09:37.067 --> 01:09:39.633
But, she wouldn't come with me.

01:09:40.800 --> 01:09:43.067
So I just let her
in the car with dad.

01:09:43.067 --> 01:09:44.800
I watched them both drive away.

01:09:46.167 --> 01:09:47.933
I knew how drunk Dad was.

01:09:48.767 --> 01:09:50.567
I couldn't come today because,

01:09:51.433 --> 01:09:53.167
Because I let our parents die.

01:09:54.233 --> 01:09:55.800
It's because I was angry.

01:09:55.800 --> 01:09:57.800
Because I love you guys
more than anything,

01:09:57.800 --> 01:10:00.533
And, I hope someday
you understand

01:10:00.533 --> 01:10:01.867
