01:10:01.867 --> 01:10:04.567
Because, my place in the world

01:10:04.567 --> 01:10:06.733
Is just to protect both of you,

01:10:06.733 --> 01:10:08.033
From people like them.

01:10:09.433 --> 01:10:11.100
I'm so sorry Sam.

01:10:12.667 --> 01:10:14.833
I'm sorry, I'm so sorry.

01:10:16.533 --> 01:10:17.367
Goodbye.

01:10:17.367 --> 01:10:21.900
(Distant country music)

01:10:32.067 --> 01:10:32.833
