01:10:32.833 --> 01:10:34.567
[Voiceover] Brian.

01:10:38.433 --> 01:10:39.867
Brian.

01:10:42.767 --> 01:10:44.300
Brian.

01:10:45.700 --> 01:10:47.700
This way, Brian.

01:10:52.700 --> 01:10:55.867
How could you not
recognize your own father?

01:10:56.467 --> 01:10:58.767
Your own (mumbling),

01:10:58.767 --> 01:11:01.133
Your never-ending nightmare.

01:11:01.867 --> 01:11:03.100
Right now...

01:11:03.700 --> 01:11:06.267
