afraid of losing us.

01:12:22.133 --> 01:12:23.900
You're just afraid
of losing our fear.

01:12:24.300 --> 01:12:25.733
[Voiceover] You think
you can destroy me

01:12:25.733 --> 01:12:27.067
With that?

01:12:28.267 --> 01:12:29.700
Seems simple enough.

01:12:30.267 --> 01:12:32.067
