you turn off the lights?

01:12:32.800 --> 01:12:34.233
You just press the
off switch, right?

01:12:34.233 --> 01:12:37.633
[Voiceover] Foolish boy,
you think it is that simple?

01:12:38.233 --> 01:12:40.967
Yeah, it is that simple.

01:12:41.967 --> 01:12:44.300
And I only have one
thing left to say to you.

01:12:45.300 --> 01:12:46.633
From the very,

01:12:47.433 --> 01:12:49.100
